      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re dwelling in the house of God,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The church life glorious."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The shrinking-back, low Christian life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Is not the life for us!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re passing through the Holy Place"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Of mind, emotion, will;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re dwelling in the Holiest"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Where God our being fills."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re under the New Covenant,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "With glorious items, three:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The law of life, spontaneous,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Transforming utterly;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We are His people, He’s our God—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, bless’d reality;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We all are fully able now"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To know God inwardly."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A supplement God added then;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This item we must know:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ Jesus did put sin away"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Two thousand years ago."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "No memory of sin at all,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It’s hist’ry, done and gone;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In spirit now the law of life"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Will take us swiftly on."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Two things accomplished by our Lord"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "On Calvary’s cross, we see:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The law of life, the end of sin!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our God’s economy."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Since all His work was finished there,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He entered into rest;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now on the throne He prays that we"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Will take our full bequest."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ll drop our former concepts, Lord,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To take this finished way;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Appropriating each bequest,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ll praise You more each day."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ll heed our High Priest’s inward call—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Come forward!” to the end—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Until we reach the final goal;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The New Jerusalem!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    }
  ],
